</ul><div class="borderContent1"><div class="hdr"><h1>Have a question? We’re here to help.</h1>
<div class="horzLine"></div><div id="lft"><h2 id="call-us" class="firstline">Call Us</h2>

<p>Whenever you have a question or need help, just give us a call!</p>
<ul><li class="singlepoint"><TEL>1-800 ROYAL 5-3</TEL> (<TEL>1-800-769-2553</TEL>)</li>
</ul>
<p>Our dedicated, bilingual customer service representatives are available 24/7 and can take care of all your banking needs for both <ORG>RBC Bank</ORG> and <ORG>RBC Royal Bank</ORG> accounts. They can not only help you open an account, but can also offer financial guidance, answer questions and address any concerns you may have!</p>

<p>And, our representatives have access to translators for other languages beyond English and French.</p>
<div class="horzLine"><h2 id="email">Send Us a Message</h2>
<dl class="faqlook"><dt class="active"><span><h3>If you are an <ORG>RBC Bank</ORG> client...</h3>
</span></dt><dd>
<p>...and have access to RBC Bank Online Banking, sign in and send us a secure message.</p>

<p><span class="button button-primary"><span><a href="https://www1.rbcbankusa.com/cgi-bin/rbaccess/rbunxcgi?F6=1&amp;F7=NS&amp;F21=IB&amp;F22=CN&amp;REQUEST=CenturaClientSignin&amp;LANGUAGE=ENGLISH">Sign in to Online Banking to send a message</a></span></span></p><img src="/files/static/uos/images/buttons/chevron.gif" height="12" alt="" width="12"/>
<div class="clearFloats"><dl class="faqs"><dt class="followFloat"><span><h3>If you are not an <ORG>RBC Bank</ORG> client...</h3>
</span></dt><dd>
<p>...and don’t have access to RBC Bank Online Banking, fill out the form below to send us your question or general inquiry. We will respond to your message within&#160;48 hours, excluding weekends and all U.S. legal holidays. Please be advised that any information sent through this form is not considered secure* and privacy cannot be ensured. Therefore, <span>we ask that you not include any confidential information such as passwords, bank account numbers, credit card numbers, or other account details</span> .</p>

<p><b class="contentframework-required-asterisk">*</b> Required Information</p>
